## Living Design 3.5 Component Inventory

### Available Components (USE THESE!)

#### Buttons & Actions
- ✅ `Button.tsx` - All button needs (primary, secondary, tertiary, destructive)
- ✅ `ButtonGroup.tsx` - Multiple buttons layout
- ✅ `IconButton.tsx` - Icon-only buttons (if available)

#### Data Display
- ✅ `tag.tsx` - Status tags and labels
- ✅ `olq-tag.tsx` - OLQ percentage badges
- ✅ `badge.tsx` - Notification badges

#### Overlays
- ✅ `popover.tsx` - Popovers with arrow support
- ✅ `dialog.tsx` - Modal dialogs
- ✅ `alert-dialog.tsx` - Confirmation dialogs

#### Forms
- ✅ `select.tsx` - Dropdown selects
- ✅ `input.tsx` - Text inputs
- ✅ `checkbox.tsx` - Checkboxes
- ✅ `calendar.tsx` - Date picker

#### Navigation
- ✅ `Menu.tsx` - Dropdown menus

#### Panels & Drawers
- ✅ **ALL panels MUST be resizable** - See `guidelines/Panel.md` for complete spec
- **REQUIRED**: Min width 420px, Max width 800px (or responsive)
- **REQUIRED**: Resize handle on left edge with visual indicator
- **REQUIRED**: localStorage persistence of user's preferred width
- **REQUIRED**: Responsive behavior for small screens

### Component Usage Stats

Last updated: 2025-01-22

- Button: ✅ Standardized across 7+ files
- Tag: ✅ Implemented with LD 3.5 tokens
- OLQTag: ✅ Implemented with LD 3.5 tokens
- ButtonGroup: ✅ Available
- Popover: ✅ Available with arrow support
- Panel: ✅ Resizable pattern established (see RecommendationsPanel.tsx)

